<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٨:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وَالسَّمَاءِ ذَاتِ الرَّجْعِ <span class="c2">(١١)</span> وَالْأَرْضِ ذَاتِ الصَّدْعِ <span class="c2">(١٢)</span> إِنَّهُ لَقَوْلٌ فَصْلٌ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span> وَمَا هُوَ بِالْهَزْلِ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[الطارق: ١١ - ١٤]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{ذَاتِ الرَّجْعِ}</span>: <span class="c2">«سَحَابٌ يَرْجِعُ بِالْمَطَرِ»</span>،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{ذَاتِ الصَّدْعِ}</span>: <span class="c2">«تَتَصَدَّعُ بِالنَّبَاتِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص١٤٣:</span> <span class="c3">{إِنَّهُ لَقَوْلٌ فَصْلٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«حَقٌّ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{وَمَا هُوَ بِالهَزْلِ}</span>: <span class="c2">«بِاللَّعِبِ»</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>